        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I imagine that I will be professor at university. I would have done my doctorat. My son will be at university. My daughter will be 15 years.In 10 years I speak perfect English and I understand it perfect. My write will be fluent. I hope... but there is still a lot of work!!!  The work in my house will be finished. My annexe will be build and my bathroom will be great. I also hope that I will have traveled and discovered the news continents and the news cultures. And I hope that I will always be happy like now or better and my family too.</p>
            </div>
